Package com.cigital.insecurepay.service.BO

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountBO
    AccountBO is POJO to store basic account information for the user.
    ChangePasswordBO
    ChangePasswordBO is POJO to store username and password for the user.
    CustomerBO
    CustomerBO is POJO to store all account information from account management for the user.
    ForgotPasswordBO
    ForgotPasswordBO is POJO to store details sent by the user for ForgotPasswordService.
    LoginBO
    LoginBO is POJO to store the user credentials for the user.
    LoginValidationBO
    LoginValidationBO is POJO to validate the user for the user.
    TransactionBO
    TransactionBO is POJO to account transaction details being retrieved for the user.
    TransferFundsBO
    TransferFundsBO is POJO to store details of the transfer being made for the user.
